Legendary musician and qualified lawyer Steve Kekana has been awarded an honorary doctorate in Philosophy by the University of South Africa. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Legendary musician and qualified lawyer, Steve Kekana has been awarded an honorary doctorate in Philosophy by the University of South Africa. The Take Your Love hitmaker says this is a dream come true. READ: Anti-apartheid activist receives honoury doctorate Dr Kekana speaks to eNCA's Morena Mothupi about his latest achievement.